{
  "_comment": "收入概览-KPI 卡片模块：顶部 6 张 KPI 卡（含迷你趋势）。用于页面第一排卡片数据源。响应字段为后端 snake_case；页面当前 `mock.ts` 为 camelCase，联调时在 `fetch` 或适配层映射为前端类型。",
  "fieldDescription": {
    "request": {
      "t_date": {
        "type": "string",
        "required": true,
        "description": "日期（YYYY-MM-DD）。"
      },
      "s_app_id": {
        "type": "string",
        "required": false,
        "description": "应用（含部署版本与终端）。空字符串/\"all\" 表示全部。"
      },
      "platform": {
        "type": "string",
        "required": false,
        "enum": ["all", "android", "ios"],
        "description": "终端平台。all 表示全部。"
      },
      "s_country_code": {
        "type": "string",
        "required": false,
        "description": "国家代码（US/GB/DE...）。\"all\" 表示全部。"
      },
      "app_version": {
        "type": "string",
        "required": false,
        "description": "应用版本。\"all\" 表示全部。"
      }
    },
    "response": {
      "kpi_list": {
        "type": "RevenueOverviewKpiCard[]",
        "required": true,
        "description": "KPI 卡片列表。"
      }
    },
    "RevenueOverviewKpiCard": {
      "s_id": { "type": "string", "required": true, "description": "卡片 id。" },
      "s_title": { "type": "string", "required": true, "description": "卡片标题。" },
      "s_primary_value": {
        "type": "string",
        "required": true,
        "description": "主值（格式化字符串）。"
      },
      "s_sub_left_label": { "type": "string", "required": true, "description": "副指标左标签。" },
      "s_sub_left_value": {
        "type": "string",
        "required": true,
        "description": "副指标左值（格式化字符串）。"
      },
      "s_sub_right_label": { "type": "string", "required": true, "description": "副指标右标签。" },
      "s_sub_right_value": {
        "type": "string",
        "required": true,
        "description": "副指标右值（格式化字符串）。"
      },
      "b_trend_up": { "type": "boolean", "required": true, "description": "趋势是否上升。" },
      "s_trend_percent_text": {
        "type": "string",
        "required": true,
        "description": "趋势文案（如：↑ 8.3% vs 昨日）。"
      },
      "d_spark_list": {
        "type": "number[]",
        "required": true,
        "description": "迷你趋势序列（数值数组）。"
      },
      "s_accent": {
        "type": "string",
        "required": true,
        "enum": ["blue", "teal", "purple", "amber", "green", "indigo"],
        "description": "卡片配色。"
      }
    }
  },
  "sampleRequest": {
    "t_date": "2026-03-05",
    "s_app_id": "weather5",
    "platform": "all",
    "s_country_code": "all",
    "app_version": "all"
  },
  "sampleResponse": {
    "kpi_list": [
      {
        "s_id": "kpi_total",
        "s_title": "总收入",
        "s_primary_value": "$2,855.05",
        "s_sub_left_label": "广告",
        "s_sub_left_value": "$2,768.58",
        "s_sub_right_label": "付费",
        "s_sub_right_value": "$86.47",
        "b_trend_up": true,
        "s_trend_percent_text": "↑ 8.3% vs 昨日",
        "d_spark_list": [2100, 2250, 1980, 2400, 2650, 2768, 2855],
        "s_accent": "blue"
      }
    ]
  },
  "api": {
    "url": "POST /api/v1/datacenter/analysis/business-insight/revenue-overview/kpi",
    "method": "POST",
    "priority": "P0",
    "requestBody": "t_date, s_app_id, platform, s_country_code, app_version（均为 body 字段）",
    "responseBody": "kpi_list (RevenueOverviewKpiCard[])"
  },
  "apiSuggestion": {
    "notes": [
      "所有金额字段建议用 number（money_*/d_*）返回，前端负责格式化；本契约 sample 为对齐原型，主值等可为预格式化 string。",
      "platform 建议只接受 all/android/ios（终端平台，与广告平台 source/n_source 区分）。",
      "与 `mock.ts` 中 `RevenueOverviewKpiCard`（id/title/primaryValue…）命名不一致时，在接入层做字段映射即可。"
    ]
  }
}
